	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wanted to let you all know that I'm going to be name dropping this community at a speech I've been invited to give for the military in Hawaii!<br /><br />A portion of the speech is how I found inspiration and solutions to current problems through the accomplishments and retro-innovations of this community!  <br /><br />Here is a little excerpt:<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">&quot;And what I discovered was that they were doing more than just making games, they pushing against the limits of the antiquated hardware to areas that it had never gone before.  They were decompiling and dissecting old games line by line, breaking the processors down cycle by cycle, and creating new compression algorithms to squeeze more and more into 2 kilobytes of working RAM; they were 'retro-innovating'&quot;</div><br /><br />So keep doing what you are doing!  You are AWESOME!

		

